# Discovery Medicine

Discovery Medicine is an open-access medical journal established in 2001. It is abstracted and indexed in [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=%22Discov+Med%22%5Bjour%5D&size=50 MEDLINE]/[https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=%22Discov+Med%22%5Bjour%5D&size=50 PubMed]. The editor-in-chief is Jun-Li Liu ([https://muhc.ca/research Research Institute of McGill University Health Center]). According to the Journal Citation Reports, the journal has a 2022 impact factor of 1.4.
